#

Arugula and Avocado Toast

5 min
$4.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Gluten (if using regular bread)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free (if using gluten-free bread)

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

EasyHealthySnackBreakfast

Description

A fresh and vibrant toast topped with creamy avocado and peppery arugula, perfect for breakfast or a light snack.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • arugula: 1 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • olive oil: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
